text: Marijke Zeekant (born 12 December 1956) is a Dutch rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Netherlands Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Medemblik
